name: Rejuvenate
description:
rejuvenate = memulihkan
.
008
Traveling the distance along with faith mingled with ego and knowledge, lulled by the desire for the unlimited desires. Tired and dizzy, sick and emotional, the more distance to the roots where we grow, and link the relationship between ourselves and true happiness. Remembering to come back for the sake of medicine for all pains and the noise of a journey, sipping the warm scent of a wise old tree providing a lush and sincere shade.
